      "description": "Looking for a practical, budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it's fully functional and ready to drive, but does show its age with some visible wear on the exterior and interior. You'll notice some cosmetic imperfections and signs of everyday use, but the mechanicals are holding up and it offers solid everyday transportation. A great pick for someone who needs reliable wheels without the premium price tag!",
