    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and is priced to reflect that honestly. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a decent shine with only minor surface scratches and small blemishes consistent with normal use. There are no major dents or rust concerns, though it's not a showroom-perfect finish. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on the seats and surfaces that you'd expect from a regularly used vehicle. All major mechanical systems are in good working order \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and the brakes feel responsive. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is a solid, dependable used car that has been maintained adequately and will serve its next owner well without requiring immediate significant repairs. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you so you can make a fully informed decision. The exterior has sustained significant damage over the years \u2014 you'll find multiple deep scratches across various panels, several noticeable dents on the doors and bumpers, and paint that has faded and chipped in numerous areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn and stained upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and general wear throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 expect to budget for repairs after purchase. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or simply needs basic transportation and is comfortable with its current state. We are pricing it accordingly to reflect its condition honestly.",
      "price": 4000.0,
