      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet your next adventure partner \u2014 a road-tested companion with a story written in every mile. This beauty carries the confidence of a car that's been lived in and loved, with a presence that turns heads and a ride that reminds you why you fell in love with driving in the first place. The interior tells tales of journeys taken, while the exterior wears its character with quiet pride. Mechanically sound and ready for the open road, this is the kind of car that becomes part of your family from the moment you turn the key. Don't let this one slip away.",
      "price": 33000.0,
